data.description: Want a country feel home but minutes away from town? You've found the perfect home. This beautiful 3 bed 2 bath home is turn-key ready. Wood-look ceramic tile throughout home. Carpet flooring upstairs. Open floor plan concept with immaculate kitchen with custom cabinets, 36'' Viking oven and gas stove, farmhouse sink and stackable microwave-oven. Gas fireplace with shelving on both sides. His and her closets in master bedroom. Jetted tub and walk-in shower in master bath. Garage is heated and cooled with an apartment inside with kitchen. Big workshop out back.
